title: Off-duty Alabama reserve deputy accused of posing as officer, making illegal traffic stop
text:
Published By: Al.com: Montgomery - Today 
A former reserve sheriff's deputy for Henry County is charged with impersonating a peace officer in connection with an illegal traffic stop ...
